uccess based on service to others, not at the expense of others.', 63634, 0), (491337, 'A successful man is one who can lay a firm foundation with the bricks others have thrown at him.', 57294, 0), (491338, 'Always bear in mind that your own resolution to succeed is more important than any other.', 1012, 0), (491339, 'Success makes so many people hate you. I wish it wasn''t that way. It would be wonderful to enjoy success without seeing envy in the eyes of those around you.', 1, 0), (491340, 'Before you are a leader, success is all about growing yourself. When you become a leader, success is all about growing others.', 10103, 0), (491341, 'One important key to success is self-confidence. An important key to self-confidence is preparation.', 52297, 0), (491342, 'Success usually comes to those who are too busy to be looking for it.', 1049, 0), (491343, 'The successful man will profit from his mistakes and try again in a different way.', 1005, 0), (491344, 'If you wish to be a success in the world, promise everything, deliver nothing.', 1702, 0), (491345, 'Success is almost totally dependent upon drive and persistence. The extra energy required to make another effort or try another approach is the secret of winning.', 1391, 0), (491346, 'The key to success is action, and the essential in action is perseverance.', 67071, 0), (491347, 'Desire is the key to motivation, but it''s the determination and commitment to unrelenting pursuit of your goal - a commitment to excellence - that will enable you to attain the success you seek.', 4657, 0), (491348, 'Success is about dedication. You may not be where you want to be or do what you want to do when you''re on the journey. But you''ve got to be willing to have vision and foresight that leads you to an incredible end.', 68120, 0), (491349, 'Do something you really like, and hopefully it pays the rent. As far as I''m concerned, that''s success.', 21291, 0), (491350, 'I''m always asked, ''What''s the secret to success?'' But ther